data.description: This spacious 3 bed 2 bath home provides plenty of space which includes  a large  flex room. The extra space  can be used as  formal dining or den. Split floor plan and large breakfast nook. Kitchen has plenty of counter space with ample cabinetry.   Master bathroom has a nicely remodeled walk-in shower and  spacious walk-in closet.   Home is located very close the Arizona City Lake.
